The "Converting circular structure to JSON" error is caused by `JSON.stringify` failing on objects that contain circular references. In this context, it is likely happening inside the `sanitizeForFirebase` function or `saveLocal` when attempting to process complex objects (possibly returned from Firestore snapshots or containing DOM event references inadvertently).

