The error `Uncaught TypeError: Converting circular structure to JSON` occurs when trying to serialize objects containing circular references or non-serializable data (like internal Firebase objects) to `localStorage`.

In `services/storageService.ts`, I will:
1.  Update `saveLocal` to use a safe serialization method that handles circular references.
2.  Replace the simple `JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(data))` in `sanitizeForFirebase` with a robust recursive function that strips out circular references and undefined values before sending to Firestore.

